You could have been in Paris tonight.
Paris. Just as you've always remembered her.
Or just as you've always dreamed she would be.
Paris. A world of high life and haut couture.
A world of lights and sounds and gardens and
spires and a river called the Seine. Above all, a
world of romance that will endure long, long
after you've come home again.
So the next time Paris tempts you, take off
with the world's most experienced airline.
En route. you can pay Paris and yourself the
compliment of flying First-Class President Spe-
cial. It's a truly special world of incomparable
cuisine by Maxim's of Paris, famous wines, un-
common service. and a very real sense of being
above it all.
Of course, you can fly Economy, if you wish.
And you can go to other European cities, if you
wish. As a matter of fact, we fly straight through
HOLIDAY / JUNE
to 27 of them from the U.S.A., twice as many
as anyone else. Call a Pan Am Travel Agent or
call us direct.
Then relax and enjoy the good feeling that
comes from flying the best there is.
Vive la difference!
World's most experienced airline
